=== English Version ===

0. Definitions
- "Server Union" (abbr: SU): Server union within Discord Japan community
- "SUMDA": This software (formerly SAUMDA)
- "SUMDA Account": User info registered in database ("DB") including login password
- "User": SU organization operating member or SU member with software access
- "Administrator": DB admin or SUMDA account with admin privileges
- "DB": Database

1. Permission Conditions
**SU organization use ONLY**. All other use strictly prohibited.

2. Usage Restrictions  
Following persons **PROHIBITED** from using this software:
- Discord users outside SU organization
- Non-Discord users
- Those without DB operation privileges

**Unauthorized use = data breach. Legal action will be taken.**

